channel.title: Heritage by Tornait [Playlist]
channel.description:
Tornait here. Just uploaded a new playlist/ep of my... forgotten stuff. Like the stuff that basically nobody is paying attention to. Makes me sad, stuff just stagnating on my SoundCloud account... But now I made all that stuff into one nice, efficient playlist. Hope you enjoy all this... Other stuff that I do.
https://soundcloud.com/tornait-jaybird/sets/heritage-tornaits-forgotten
